snippet.title: Cloud Jumpers Free Multiplayer Game - Teaser 2
snippet.description:
We work on a 8 Player Multiplayer game. 

Bring your Potato to the Goal and avoid the obstacles and Slap other potatoes.
New Arena Mode included.



free version on https://discord.gg/CsuH5N3
